### Default button dropdown

```jsx
<div>
  <Dropdown text="Default dropdown" look="primary" soft>
    <p>Example dropdown content ...</p>
  </Dropdown>
  <br />
  <br />
  <Dropdown text="Dropdown with headings" look="primary" soft>
    <DropdownHeading>Dropdown heading #1</DropdownHeading>
    Example dropdown content...
    <DropdownHeading>Dropdown heading #2</DropdownHeading>
    Example dropdown content...
  </Dropdown>
</div>
```

### Button dropdown sizes

```jsx
<div className="flex gap-1">
  <Dropdown text="Small dropdown" dropdownSize="small" look="primary" soft>
    <DropdownHeading>Small dropdown menu: 130px wide</DropdownHeading>
  </Dropdown>
  <Dropdown text="Medium dropdown" dropdownSize="medium" look="primary" soft>
    <DropdownHeading>Medium (default) dropdown menu: 190px wide</DropdownHeading>
  </Dropdown>
  <Dropdown text="Large dropdown" dropdownSize="large" look="primary" soft>
    <DropdownHeading>Large dropdown menu: 250px wide</DropdownHeading>
  </Dropdown>
</div>
```
